companyName: ETRACS Montly Pay 2xLeveraged US High Dividend Low Volatility ETN due September 30 2044
description:
The investment seeks a return linked to the performance of the price return version of the Solactive US High Dividend Low Volatility Index (the “index”).
 The Securities provide a monthly compounded two times leveraged long exposure to the performance of the index, reduced by the Accrued Fees. The index is designed to measure the performance of 40 dividend yielding, relatively lower volatility index constituent Securities from the universe of the largest 1,000 U.S. listed stocks by market capitalization.
